headlines.description: West Ham United boosted their bid for European qualification as they beat 10-man Everton 2-1.
headlines.shortLinkText: Cresswell, Bowen strike as West Ham sink 10-man Everton

headlines.description: Tottenham Hotspur stepped up their Champions League qualification bid as they rallied to an emphatic 5-1 victory over Newcastle United on Sunday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Spurs rout Newcastle to step up top four bid
